{"text_id":155743,"tokens":["When"," it"," comes"," to"," making"," important"," decisions",","," it"," can"," be"," tempting"," to"," rely"," on"," our"," own"," judgment"," and"," experiences","."," After"," all",","," who"," knows"," us"," better"," than"," ourselves","?"," However",","," seeking"," advice"," from"," multiple"," sources"," can"," provide"," a"," wealth"," of"," benefits"," that"," can"," ultimately"," lead"," to"," better"," decision","-","making",".","\n\n","One"," of"," the"," most"," significant"," advantages"," of"," seeking"," advice"," from"," multiple"," sources"," is"," the"," ability"," to"," gain"," a"," wider"," perspective","."," When"," we"," limit"," ourselves"," to"," our"," own"," experiences"," and"," opinions",","," we"," can"," easily"," become"," blinded"," to"," other"," viewpoints"," and"," possibilities","."," By"," consulting"," with"," a"," diverse"," group"," of"," people",","," we"," can"," expose"," ourselves"," to"," a"," range"," of"," different"," perspectives",","," ideas",","," and"," approaches"," that"," we"," may"," not"," have"," considered"," on"," our"," own",".","\n\n","For"," example",","," when"," I"," was"," deciding"," on"," which"," college"," to"," attend",","," I"," sought"," advice"," from"," a"," variety"," of"," sources",","," including"," my"," parents",","," teachers",","," and"," friends","."," While"," my"," parents"," encouraged"," me"," to"," attend"," a"," well","-","respected"," university"," that"," was"," known"," for"," its"," rigorous"," academic"," programs",","," my"," friends"," suggested"," a"," smaller",","," liberal"," arts"," college"," that"," offered"," a"," more"," intimate"," learning"," environment","."," By"," considering"," both"," options",","," I"," was"," able"," to"," weigh"," the"," pros"," and"," cons"," of"," each"," and"," ultimately"," make"," an"," informed"," decision"," that"," was"," best"," for"," me",".","\n\n","Another"," benefit"," of"," seeking"," advice"," from"," multiple"," sources"," is"," the"," ability"," to"," gain"," valuable"," insights"," and"," expertise","."," When"," we"," surround"," ourselves"," with"," people"," who"," have"," different"," skills",","," experiences",","," and"," areas"," of"," expertise",","," we"," can"," tap"," into"," their"," knowledge"," and"," insights"," to"," help"," inform"," our"," decisions",".","\n\n","For"," instance",","," when"," I"," was"," starting"," my"," own"," business",","," I"," sought"," advice"," from"," several"," successful"," entrepreneurs"," and"," business"," owners","."," While"," some"," offered"," advice"," on"," financial"," management"," and"," accounting",","," others"," provided"," insights"," on"," marketing"," and"," sales"," strategies","."," By"," taking"," in"," their"," collective"," wisdom",","," I"," was"," able"," to"," create"," a"," more"," well","-","rounded"," and"," effective"," business"," plan"," that"," took"," into"," account"," a"," variety"," of"," factors"," and"," considerations",".","\n\n","Seeking"," advice"," from"," multiple"," sources"," can"," also"," help"," us"," to"," identify"," potential"," blind"," spots"," and"," areas"," of"," weakness","."," When"," we"," rely"," solely"," on"," our"," own"," judgment",","," we"," run"," the"," risk"," of"," making"," decisions"," based"," on"," incomplete"," or"," inaccurate"," information","."," By"," consulting"," with"," others",","," we"," can"," identify"," areas"," where"," we"," may"," be"," lacking"," in"," knowledge"," or"," expertise"," and"," take"," steps"," to"," address"," those"," gaps",".","\n\n","For"," example",","," when"," I"," was"," preparing"," for"," a"," job"," interview",","," I"," sought"," advice"," from"," several"," colleagues"," who"," had"," previously"," held"," similar"," positions","."," While"," some"," offered"," advice"," on"," how"," to"," answer"," common"," interview"," questions",","," others"," provided"," insights"," on"," company"," culture"," and"," expectations","."," By"," taking"," in"," their"," feedback",","," I"," was"," able"," to"," identify"," areas"," where"," I"," needed"," to"," improve"," my"," skills"," and"," knowledge",","," and"," I"," was"," ultimately"," able"," to"," land"," the"," job",".","\n\n","Perhaps"," most"," importantly",","," seeking"," advice"," from"," multiple"," sources"," can"," help"," us"," to"," build"," relationships"," and"," establish"," a"," network"," of"," support","."," When"," we"," reach"," out"," to"," others"," for"," advice"," and"," guidance",","," we"," demonstrate"," our"," willingness"," to"," learn"," and"," grow","."," This"," can"," help"," to"," establish"," trust"," and"," rapport",","," and"," can"," lead"," to"," long","-","lasting"," relationships"," that"," can"," benefit"," us"," in"," both"," our"," personal"," and"," professional"," lives",".","\n\n","For"," instance",","," when"," I"," was"," facing"," a"," difficult"," personal"," situation",","," I"," sought"," advice"," from"," several"," trusted"," friends"," and"," family"," members","."," While"," some"," offered"," emotional"," support"," and"," encouragement",","," others"," provided"," practical"," advice"," and"," resources","."," By"," taking"," in"," their"," advice"," and"," support",","," I"," was"," able"," to"," navigate"," the"," situation"," with"," greater"," ease"," and"," confidence",".","\n\n","Of"," course",","," seeking"," advice"," from"," multiple"," sources"," is"," not"," without"," its"," challenges","."," It"," can"," be"," time","-","consuming"," and"," may"," require"," us"," to"," sift"," through"," a"," lot"," of"," conflicting"," or"," irrelevant"," information","."," However",","," by"," approaching"," the"," process"," with"," an"," open"," mind"," and"," a"," willingness"," to"," learn",","," we"," can"," reap"," the"," many"," benefits"," of"," seeking"," advice"," from"," a"," diverse"," group"," of"," people",".","\n\n","In"," conclusion",","," seeking"," advice"," from"," multiple"," sources"," can"," provide"," a"," wealth"," of"," benefits"," when"," it"," comes"," to"," making"," important"," decisions","."," By"," gaining"," a"," wider"," perspective",","," tapping"," into"," valuable"," insights"," and"," expertise",","," identifying"," potential"," blind"," spots",","," and"," building"," relationships",","," we"," can"," make"," more"," informed"," and"," effective"," decisions"," that"," will"," serve"," us"," well"," in"," both"," our"," personal"," and"," professional"," lives","."," So",","," the"," next"," time"," you"," are"," faced"," with"," a"," difficult"," decision",","," consider"," reaching"," out"," to"," a"," variety"," of"," people"," for"," advice"," and"," guidance","."," You"," may"," be"," surprised"," at"," just"," how"," much"," you"," can"," learn"," and"," grow"," as"," a"," result","."],"sub_source":"outfox","model":"mixtral-8x7b","label":1}